+        0516c9e: Changed indented content processing to use block parser instead of manual paragraph splitting. 
+        Replaced _PARAGRAPH_SPLIT logic with BlockState initialization and block.parse() call.
+        Children tokens now preserve full block structure (lists/headers/etc) instead of being limited to paragraphs.
+    """
